Name: HERO-E
About the game: Explore a world of underground caves, rescuing swimmers who have been abducted by a mysterious black hand ... Battle against dangerous creatures and find your beloved ... Can You defeat to black hand? 20 Action-packed Levels In Intricate Mazes ... Use dynamite to blast the rocks and make your way ... Care!, dangers lurk anywhere ... Spiders, Bats, Snakes, Poisonous Moths,Carnivorous Plants and many other hazards... Hurry! the clock is ticking, and you can run out of power. Will these caves turn into your tomb? or you will become a real HERO-E?
